# 🎯 PROMPT COMPLETO: Recrear Chill Chess Club en Next.js + TypeScript

**INSTRUCCIONES PARA LA IA:**

Necesito que crees un sitio web profesional desde cero usando Next.js 14, TypeScript y Tailwind CSS. Debes seguir EXACTAMENTE las especificaciones de este documento. No omitas ningún detalle.

---

## 📋 ESPECIFICACIONES TÉCNICAS

### Stack Tecnológico (OBLIGATORIO)

```json

{

  "framework": "Next.js 14 (App Router)",

  "language": "TypeScript",

  "styling": "Tailwind CSS",

  "i18n": "next-intl",

  "animations": "Framer Motion",

  "forms": "React Hook Form + Zod",

  "icons": "React Icons (Font Awesome)",

  "deployment": "Vercel"

}

```

### Comandos de Instalación

```bash

npx create-next-app@latest chill-chess-club --typescript --tailwind --app --no-src-dir

cd chill-chess-club

npm install next-intl framer-motion react-hook-form zod react-icons

```

---

## 🎨 DISEÑO Y ESTILO

### Paleta de Colores (EXACTA)

```typescript

// tailwind.config.ts

const colors = {

  primary: {

    DEFAULT: "#ec4899", // Pink-500

    dark: "#be185d", // Pink-700

    light: "#f9a8d4", // Pink-300

  },

  secondary: {

    DEFAULT: "#8b5cf6", // Purple-500

    dark: "#6d28d9", // Purple-700

    light: "#c4b5fd", // Purple-300

  },

  accent: {

    DEFAULT: "#f59e0b", // Amber-500

    dark: "#d97706", // Amber-600

  },

  dark: {

    bg: "#0f172a", // Slate-900

    darker: "#020617", // Slate-950

    card: "#1e293b", // Slate-800

  },

  text: {

    primary: "#f8fafc", // Slate-50

    secondary: "#cbd5e1", // Slate-300

  },

};

```

### Tipografía

```typescript

// app/layout.tsx

import { Playfair_Display, Roboto } from "next/font/google";

const playfair = Playfair_Display({

  subsets: ["latin"],

  variable: "--font-playfair",

  display: "swap",

});

const roboto = Roboto({

  weight: ["300", "400", "500", "700"],

  subsets: ["latin"],

  variable: "--font-roboto",

  display: "swap",

});

// Usar:

// Headings: font-playfair

// Body: font-roboto

```

### Gradientes

```css

.gradient-primary {

  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ec4899 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);

}

.gradient-secondary {

  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #ec4899 100%);

}

```

